    IRuleBasedValueCont: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This represents the values of a compound primitive (CURVE, MAP, CUBOID, CUBE_4, CUBE_5, VAL_BLK) or an array.

        IValueList getSwArraysize()
        Query the undirectional one-to-one aggregation swArraysize.

        This attribute defines the size of each dimension for compound primitivies CURVE, MAP, CUBOID, CUBE_4, CUBE_5, COM_AXIS, RES_AXIS, VAL_BLK, STRING. For each dimension one value has to be defined, e.g. one in case of COM_AXIS and two or more in case of MAP.
